**Scheme Implementation (Acquisition by Dollarama Inc.)**  
- **Implementation Date:** 22 July 2025  
- **Scheme Consideration:** $5.91 cash per share paid to shareholders as of 15 July 2025.  
- **Special Dividend:** $0.77 (fully franked) per share paid on 14 July 2025 to shareholders as of 7 July 2025.  
- **Delisting:** ASX suspension effective 1 July 2025; removal from official ASX list after close on 23 July 2025.  

**No further material information identified.**
